{
  "text": "The development of the three FDA-approved multivalent prophylactic human papillomavirus (HPV) vaccines has been because of the discovery of HPV infection as the cause of all cervical cancer [CITATION_1] . The three prophylactic HPV vaccines have shown high efficacy for prevention of HPV infection [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
